      "message": "Instead of checking the type against a set of configured types, check against the private types, i.e. something like:\n    private ToscaProperty validateToscaProperty(List<DataTypeDefinition> privateDataTypes, final ToscaProperty toscaProperty, final ToscaProperty toscaProperty2) {\n        final Optional<DataTypeDefinition> match = privateDataTypes.stream().filter(dataType -> dataType.getName().equals(toscaProperty.getType())).findFirst();\n\n        if(match.isPresent()){\n            return toscaProperty;\n        }\n\n        return toscaProperty2;\n    }",
